ur."},"groundingChunkIndices": [3,9,0]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 349,"endIndex": 442,"text": "Sea otters have the thickest fur of any animal, with up to one million hairs per square inch."},"groundingChunkIndices": [4,7]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 443,"endIndex": 551,"text": "*   **Diet:** They are active hunters that primarily eat fish, but also consume frogs, birds, and shellfish."},"groundingChunkIndices": [3,0]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 552,"endIndex": 638,"text": "Sea otters are famous for using stones as tools to crack open shells on their bellies."},"groundingChunkIndices": [11,3]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 639,"endIndex": 793,"text": "*   **Habitat:** Most species live in freshwater (rivers, lakes, and wetlands), while sea otters and marine otters live in saltwater coastal environments."},"groundingChunkIndices": [1,2]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 795,"endIndex": 820,"text": "### Interesting Behaviors"},"groundingChunkIndices": [11]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 821,"endIndex": 998,"text": "*   **Playfulness:** Otters are known for "sliding" down muddy or snowy banks into the water and playing with small stones, which helps them develop survival and hunting skills."},"groundingChunkIndices": [1,3,9]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 999,"endIndex": 1113,"text": "*   **Social Life:** While many river otters are solitary, sea otters often rest in large groups called **rafts**."},"groundingChunkIndices": [10,1,7,11]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 1207,"endIndex": 1371,"text": "*   **Breath-holding:** They are expert divers; river otters can hold their breath for up to **8 minutes**, while sea otters can stay submerged for about 5 minutes."},"groundingChunkIndices": [11,4]},{"segment": {"startIndex": 1372,"endIndex": 1524,"text": "*   **Grooming:** Because they lack a layer of blubber, otters spend hours every day grooming their fur to trap air bubbles for insulation and buoyancy."},"groundingChunkIndices": [7]}],"webSearchQueries": ["brief facts about otters","types of otters and their habitats","interesting otter behaviors and characteristics"]}}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 12,"candidatesTokenCount": 335,"totalTokenCount": 347,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 12}]},"modelVersion": "gemini-3-flash-preview","responseId": "aiuqababGbrKjuMP8aaJ4Ak"}

